                <p class="project-number">03 / Operational awareness</p>
                <h3><a href="https://yuhexin25-oss.github.io/livedelayanalysis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Live Delay Analysis Dashboard</a></h3>
                <p>The Hub Resilience Monitor combines airport operational metrics, supplemental FAA advisories, static routes, and estimated hub-impact and route-risk scores. This provides the real-time layer missing from retrospective datasets: awareness of current hub conditions and potential downstream network exposure.</p>
                <p>The dashboard distinguishes connected operational data from labeled sample fallback mode, and its scores are analytical estimates rather than FAA predictions. That provenance discipline is essential during the World Cup, when a visible delay at one airport should inform network awareness without being misreported as tournament causation.</p>
